down\n ip address 172.42.1.1/24\n!\ninterface eth1\n no shutdown\n description x1 -> dut [external]\n ip address 10.1.0.2/30\n!\ndo write\nCONFIG\nvtysh -f /tmp/config\n!\nexit 0\n"
